          "A worked version for your profile: 'Right now I'm a tech lead on a backend and platform team, where I own our public-facing API and the serverless data pipelines behind it on AWS. The work I'm proudest of is hardening that public API behind a WAF and scaling it to 40-plus partner integrations, building an SQS-Lambda-DynamoDB batch system that processes our heavy workloads asynchronously, and most recently a RAG pipeline on Bedrock. The through-line is taking ambiguous platform problems and turning them into reliable, well-instrumented systems other teams build on. I'm looking for a staff role where that scope is the core of the job, which is why this team caught my attention.'",
